The New Screen Savers 23
The Man Behind Tor
Hosted by Leo Laporte, Ron Richards
Training for Space at the bottom of the sea, the man behind TOR, and why Microsoft fans are so giddy.
Records live every Saturday at 6:00pm Eastern / 3:00pm Pacific / 22:00 UTC.
Guests: Dr. Paul Syverson, David Coan
Category: Help & How To

Microsoft's new gear, the creator of the Onion and TOR Projects, astronauts training for Space at the bottom of the sea, the best cord-cutting app you've never heard of, and it's International Light Saber Day.

The New Screen Savers will record live, every Saturday at 3PM Pacific on live.twit.tv. It will be made available for download and streaming later that evening at https://twit.tv/shows/new-screen-savers
